    "Gradient clipping and differential privacy have the potential to mitigate model poisoning attacks to some extent [13,225,285], but they usually decrease accuracy and do not provide complete mitigation.For specifc model poisoning vulnerabilities, such as backdoor attacks, there are some techniques for model inspection and sanitization, as discussed in Section 2.3.3."
